1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:09:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1759530/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1759530/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再請廣傅<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係想故弄玄虛<br />\n係怕有變數<br />\n<br />\n經過我哋小組開會<br />\n決定都講多啲<br />\n<br />\n呼籲大家到英領原因，因為我哋係英國戰線<br />\n我哋小組係英國見過mp<br />\nMp話只要有一百人內填飽灰磚<br />\n係十二月大選後會視香港正面對人道危機處理<br />\n但mp話真係要夠人先證明到有人道危機<br />\n<br />\n所以最後英政府點做<br />\n睇大家留守意志<br />\n<br />\nSource： Facebook Page -<br />\nDescendants of Victoria City"},{"pid":"892071d6d0ff3142b755a97936bc7b5d10d13c55","tid":1759543,"uid":313261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"Pandora Me既串飾細粒好多，要配同系列嘅手鍊用。Pandora Me 係針對年輕人市場，價錢平過其他系列。"},{"pid":"9fa05deba9940859765f697cb43d8c011f630952","tid":1759543,"uid":234199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9358cb351fb1e95ea9dbc42a8c233f2b18b66252","tid":1759543,"uid":274869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"唔興好耐喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇推介？"},{"pid":"e93d57ccbca6ba178d21ec69d11c16bc9a0b7710","tid":1759543,"uid":234199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892071d6d0ff3142b755a97936bc7b5d10d13c55","tid":1759543,"uid":313261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"Pandora Me既串飾細粒好多，要配同系列嘅手鍊用。Pandora Me 係針對年輕人市場，價錢平過其他系列。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"但係好少款揀"},{"pid":"8af408527b48149b9dfc66ad536d8050ea9ccb79","tid":1759543,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fa05deba9940859765f697cb43d8c011f630952","tid":1759543,"uid":234199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9358cb351fb1e95ea9dbc42a8c233f2b18b66252","tid":1759543,"uid":274869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"唔興好耐喇喎<